1. Use MongoDB as the database.
2. Backend in Golang (Gin/Fiber)
3. Frontend in TypeScript (Next.js + Tailwind CSS)
4. JWT authentication for user sessions.
5. Goroutines & WebSockets for real-time task updates.
6. Use Gemini API for chatbot development.
7. First finish the project, then add deployment steps.
8. This is a Windows machine.